Introduction

Kimi (키미), also known by her name Kim Minji (김민지) and formerly as Habin (하빈), is a South Korean rapper under J-Star Entertainment. She is a member of the girl group ONAIR and a former member of the girl groups We Girls, BULLDOK, Scarlet, Leader'S and its sub-units Leader'S G, Leader'S N and Leader'S T. She was a contestant on Produce 101, she was eliminated in episode 10 after ranking 44th place. She made her solo debut in August 25, 2017 with the digital single "I Am".
